{{#titleicon_unicode:🧾}}
Pages in this category are individual expense entries created via
[[Form:Expense]] (or directly through the form-edit flow from
[[Special:ReceiptReview]]).

For totals, filtering, and CSV export across all entries, use
[[Special:Ledger|the ledger]].

The <code>{{#titleicon_unicode:}}</code> call above sets the title icon
for every page in this category — [[Template:Expense]] auto-categorizes
expense pages here. Change the emoji here to retheme all expense
entries at once. Requires the [[mw:Extension:TitleIcon|TitleIcon]]
extension.
